import React from 'react'
import {BrowserRouter, Routes, Route} from 'react-router-dom'
import Home from './Home'
import Create from './Create'

function App() {
  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
    <Routes>
      <Route path='/' element={<Home />} />
      <Route path='/create' element={<Create />} />
    </Routes>
    </BrowserRouter>
  )
}

export default App
